high_descs: Walk to the sink straight ahead.
Pick up the fork to the right of the apples in the sink.
Move over to the left side of the sink.
Put the fork inside the mug that's behind the apples in the sink.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn right and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the mug down on the counter to the right of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To move a fork in a mug to the counter.

high_descs: Head straight and move forward to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the fork that's in the sink.
Take a step to the left with the fork, keep facing the sink.
Put the fork in the black mug that's in the sink.
Pick up the black mug in the sink.
Bring the mug with you and go right, then turn left to face the counter on the right side of the sink.
Put the mug down on the counter so it's to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Move the mug in the sink to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the metal fork that is in the sink.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the fork in the mug that is in the sink.
Pick up the mug with the fork in it.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the mug with the fork in it on the front edge of the counter to the right of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork in it on the counter.
